==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Originally, the name of the fourth concubine of the Yellow Emperor.  She was known for being really ugly.
===Noun===
{{cmn-noun|ts|pin=mómŭ|pint=mo2mu3|rs=女11}}
# a hag; an ugly woman
